OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781021473
OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,FCampaigners have opposed plans for a
OL,7,F#2billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,8,FBorders over environmental concerns.
OL,10,FSunlaws Development Company Limited
OL,11,Fwant to build the Southside Data
OL,12,FCentre on land at Clawbare Cottage in
OL,13,FLongformacus.
OL,15,FThe plans for the development on the
OL,16,FRoxburghe Estate include three two-
OL,17,Fstorey data centre buildings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
