FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781021473
OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,FWithin each building, half of the
OL,7,Fspace would be used for IT and the
OL,8,Fother half for electrical and
OL,9,Fmechanical infrastructure.
OL,11,FThe prospect of such a huge centre on
OL,12,Ftheir doorstep has alarmed the
OL,13,Fcommunities of Longformacus, Allenford
OL,14,Fand the Cranshaws.
OL,16,FJaap Roell is the Managing Director of
OL,17,FRoxburghe Estates and spoke to
OL,18,Fvisitors at the drop-in session in
OL,19,FLongformacus, he said:
OL,26,@xD@Gxw
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781021473
OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,F"Secure data centres are absolutely at
OL,7,Fthe heart of our economies and are
OL,8,Frequired for economic growth, and we
OL,9,Fdiscovered that we happen to have one
OL,10,Fof the best sites in Scotland, to
OL,11,Fcreate such a data centre.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, we have a site that can
OL,14,Feasily be connected to multiple wind
OL,15,Ffarms, as well as aJbattery energy
OL,16,Fstorage system."
OL,18,FA campaign has been launched to block
OL,19,Fthe plans amid concerns over the
OL,20,F"industrialisation" of the Lammermuir
OL,21,FHills.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
