OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781021473
OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,FCari Silver is part of the Save the
OL,7,FLammermuirs - Stop the Data Centre
OL,8,Fcampaign group opposing the proposals
OL,9,Ffor a data centre in the Scottish
OL,10,FBorders, she said:
OL,12,F"We're not anti-development. We're not
OL,13,Fanti-AI. We are not anti-technology.
OL,14,FBut we truly feel that this is a
OL,15,Fcompletely inappropriate place to
OL,16,Fbuild an industrial sized data centre."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781021473
OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,FAnother member of the campaign group,
OL,7,FZach Pygall said: "It's the size of 11
OL,8,Ffootball pitches and it's going to be
OL,9,Fcompletely covered in concrete. And it
OL,10,Fdoesn't matter if they put grass on
OL,11,Fthe roof or surrounded by a hill, it's
OL,12,Fstill a massive, massive impact on the
OL,13,Flocal environment as well as the
OL,14,Fpeople who live here."
OL,16,FThe developer says the data centre
OL,17,Frepresents a #2 billion investment in
OL,18,Fthe Scottish economy, bringing with it
OL,19,F145 long-term jobs and also bolstering
OL,20,Fthe Borders economy to the tune of
OL,21,F#12m a year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
