OL,3,C#2 billion data centre in the Scottish
OL,4,CBorders opposed by campaign group
OL,6,FA second consultation event will be
OL,7,Fstaged at Westruther Village Hall on
OL,8,FTuesday, June 10, and the developer
OL,9,Fintends to have further consultation
OL,10,Fwith the community later this year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
